name: Geek Tree 02 : Pong Down
description:
In the last century somewhere between 1972 and 1975 the technology was.. Pong! Pong! Pong!
Now artificial intelligence has taken over and, being really pissed off, it has decided to enslave old pc's and use trees to power them to play Pong with CD-rom.. But sometimes but sometimes intelligence is very artificial
